<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I think your error, dear brother, is you are still using Root...<p>

Use enstill and immobilize.  They are somewhat easier to resist, but they are also more resistant to breaking when they stick.  Immobilize also casts wonderfully fast!  Any sudden direct damage will give the mob a chance to break your roots, however...that's how the spell was meant to work.<p>

<br>
Shaar Goldentouch<br>
49th Cleric</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
